title: Dodgers finally secure third straight NL West crown
text:
> Sports Dodgers finally secure third straight NL West crown Los Angeles Dodgers pitcher Clayton Kershaw, right, hugs catcher A.J. Ellis (17) after beating the San Francisco Giants in a baseball game in San Francisco, Tuesday, Sept. 29, 2015. The Dodgers won 8-0 to clinch the National League West division. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu)
